text: :"Freystadt" is also the German names for Kisielice and Kożuchów, Poland. Freystadt is a town in Neumarkt in Bavaria. It is near the Rhine-Main-Danube Canal, 14 km southwest of Neumarkt in der Oberpfalz, and 33 km southeast of Nuremberg. ==References== Category:Neumarkt (district)
title: Freystadt
